## Chapter 1: A gentle introduction to Borf syntax and Prelude

Welcome to Borf, a domain-specific language designed for working with interaction nets. This chapter will introduce you to the basic syntax and core concepts of Borf, helping you build a foundation for more advanced topics in later chapters.
